---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <Header />

  <main class="py-8">
    <HeroSection 
      title="Privacy Policy" 
      description="Your privacy matters. Here's how we handle your data at Green Orbit Digital."
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto">

          <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Green Orbit Digital Ltd</strong> is a private limited company registered in England and Wales (Company No. 15207389).
            Our registered office is: DOCK - Space City, 75 Exploration Drive, Leicester LE4 5NU.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are a data controller under the UK General Data Protection Regulation and registered with the Information Commissioner’s Office (ICO), Registration Number: ZB640949.
          </p>

          <h2>2. What Personal Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect personal data when:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>You browse our website</li>
            <li>Your organisation uses our services</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Analytics tools like Google Analytics and GoSquared help us understand user behaviour. These tools collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>IP address and referring domain</li>
            <li>Device type, OS, screen resolution, and browser</li>
            <li>Geolocation and session data (e.g., page views, time on site)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>This data is pseudonymised and not sold. For further information, please review:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.gosquared.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GoSquared Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We also use cookies. View our full <a href="/cookie-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cookie Policy</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p>Your data may be used to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Send you marketing communications based on your preferences</li>
            <li>Serve personalised content or ads and measure campaign effectiveness</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. Sharing Your Data</h2>
          <p>We share your Website Data with select third-party services for analytics and marketing purposes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.gosquared.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GoSquared</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary. Once no longer required, it is securely deleted or anonymised. In cases where immediate deletion is not possible (e.g., backups), data is safely isolated until it can be removed.</p>

          <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>We use a range of technical and organisational measures to protect your data, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Encryption at rest and in transit</li>
            <li>Role-based access controls and secure password policies</li>
            <li>Regular staff training on data security and privacy</li>
            <li>Automated vulnerability scanning and static code analysis</li>
            <li>Mutual TLS (MTLS) and API key rotation</li>
            <li>Privacy-by-design principles in all platform development</li>
            <li>Background checks for employees with access to sensitive data</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>If you're based in the UK, EEA, or Switzerland, you may:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can also contact your local data protection authority:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="http://ec.europa.eu/justice/data-protection/bodies/authorities/index_en.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">EEA & UK Regulators</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.edoeb.admin.ch/edoeb/en/home.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Swiss Authorities</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h2>8. Do-Not-Track</h2>
          <p>
            While some browsers support "Do-Not-Track" (DNT), we do not currently respond to these signals due to lack of a universal standard. If a standard emerges, we will update our practices accordingly.
          </p>

          <h2>9. Policy Updates</h2>
          <p>
            We may revise this Privacy Policy occasionally. Significant updates will be communicated where reasonably possible.
          </p>

          <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            For any questions, concerns, or data access requests, please get in touch.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2">
              Contact Us
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Or contact the UK Information Commissioner’s Office directly:
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic text-sm">
            The Information Commissioner’s Office<br />
            Wycliffe House, Water Lane, Wilmslow, Cheshire, SK9 5AF<br />
            Phone: 0303 123 1113<br />
            <a href="https://www.ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.ico.org.uk</a>
          </address>

        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>